comments: Too much work for a 3 unit class. A LOT of reading. Multiple quizzes, discussions, and 1 midterm about every 2 weeks throughout the semester (total of 10 exams, 14 discussions, 23 case study quizzes). Quizzes & tests should have been proofread as well. Professor always had to go back & manually give credit back. Heavy workload but still got an A.
